# Design Principles

## Unique Design Style
- Maintain brand consistency with the established color scheme:
  - Deep Space (`#1C1C22`)
  - Champagne (`#D3B88C`)
  - Moonlight (`#EAEAEA`)
  - Silverstone (`#3A3A42`)
  - Coral (`#E87A90`)
- Use custom components rather than standard ones where appropriate
- Create distinctive visual elements to make the app stand out

## Visual Engagement
- Include micro-interactions and subtle animations to improve usability
- Ensure proper spacing and alignment for clean layouts
- Use high contrast between text and backgrounds for readability
- Design with attention to detail in state feedback and interactive elements

## Typography and Layout
- Use the Inter font family as the primary typeface
- Maintain clear typographic hierarchy
- Experiment with non-traditional layouts while keeping navigation intuitive
- Ensure responsive design across different screen sizes